God is gonna trouble these waters

02:33.487 --> 02:37.491
Man went down to the river

02:38.450 --> 02:43.372
Man went down to the river, Lord

02:43.455 --> 02:47.626
Man went down to the river

02:48.460 --> 02:52.130
Went down there for to pray

02:52.673 --> 02:53.674
Oh

